data.description: Welcome home to this jaw-dropping 2021 custom-built beauty in Pueblo West Acreage! As you breeze in from the paved street, your eyes will be dazzled by breathtaking mountain and Colorado topography views from all around the home.  The exterior is architecturally gorgeous, with stucco details, a covered front porch and a large walk-out deck. Stepping inside you're greeted by a spacious entryway that leads to a well-thought-out floor plan. The mudroom is adorable, complete with built-in shelves, laundry space, and a utility sink. Next up is a spacious carpeted living room that opens to a generous dining space. The adjacent kitchen is a delight, with modern soft-close cabinetry, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a window that picture frames views of Pikes Peak. Beyond the kitchen are 2 guest bedrooms with plush carpeting and more breathtaking mountain views and sit near a beautiful hall bath that boasts an extended vanity and custom ceiling-tub tiled tub/shower. On the other side of the house, you'll find the tranquil primary bedroom with a tray ceiling, plush carpeting, and a luxurious attached bath that includes a dual sink vanity, a HUGE walk-in closet, poured pan step-in shower with with more custom tiling, and a private commode closet. The unfinished basement is a blank canvas with smartly placed HVAC, plumbing systems along with a tankless water heater and a plumbed off space for a future bath.  Close to schools, shopping and more- this home is a treasure!
